印度尼西亞是发展中國家，歷史背景與南亞洲各地一樣，产业结构落后，国内工业欠发达。初期，印度尼西亞通过开发石油和其它资源，实现了粮食自给和生产自立。印度尼西亞經濟上由私人部門及政府共同主導，屬[[混合经济|混合经济]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.state.gov/r/pa/ei/bgn/2748.htm |title=Economy of Indonesia |publisher=State.gov |accessdate=2011-04-10 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/616nEadEx?url=http://www.state.gov/r/pa/ei/bgn/2748.htm |archive-date=2011-08-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。印度尼西亞為東南亞最大經濟體及[[20國集團|20國集團]]成員國<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.g20.org/about_what_is_g20.aspx |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110504233459/http://www.g20.org/about_what_is_g20.aspx |archivedate=2011-05-04 |title=What is the G-20 |publisher=G-20 |accessdate=2009-10-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，2011年[[国内生产总值|国内生产总值]]（國際匯率）為8,456.80億美元，人均国内生产总值為3,509美元，以購買力平價則為4,666美元<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.imf.org/external/pubs/ft/weo/2012/01/weodata/weorept.aspx?pr.x=26&pr.y=11&sy=2011&ey=2011&scsm=1&ssd=1&sort=country&ds=.&br=1&c=536&s=NGDPD%2CNGDPDPC%2CPPPGDP%2CPPPPC&grp=0&a= |title=Report for Selected Countries and Subjects |publisher=Imf.org |accessdate=2012-07-12 |archive-date=2021-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210508002628/https://www.imf.org/external/pubs/ft/weo/2012/01/weodata/weorept.aspx?pr.x=26&pr.y=11&sy=2011&ey=2011&scsm=1&ssd=1&sort=country&ds=.&br=1&c=536&s=NGDPD%2CNGDPDPC%2CPPPGDP%2CPPPPC&grp=0&a= |dead-url=no }}</ref>，印度尼西亞人均所得在1995年已突破1,000美元，後經亞洲金融風暴的打擊，曾短暫退至500美元以下，但2000年以來穩步成長，至2010年已約達3,000美元<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.imf.org/external/pubs/ft/weo/2012/01/weodata/weorept.aspx?sy=1994&ey=2011&ssd=1&sort=country&ds=.&br=1&pr1.x=17&pr1.y=9&c=536&s=NGDPDPC&grp=0&a=|title=Report for Selected Countries and Subjects|publisher=Imf.org|accessdate=2012-07-22|archive-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507095924/https://www.imf.org/external/pubs/ft/weo/2012/01/weodata/weorept.aspx?sy=1994&ey=2011&ssd=1&sort=country&ds=.&br=1&pr1.x=17&pr1.y=9&c=536&s=NGDPDPC&grp=0&a=|dead-url=no}}</ref>、外債比率約為21.6％<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.embassyofindonesia.org/news/2011/08/news076.htm |title=RI's Foreign Debts Safe |accessdate=2012-09-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120324100616/http://www.embassyofindonesia.org/news/2011/08/news076.htm |archivedate=2012-03-24 }}</ref>。印度尼西亞經濟以2010年的數據分析國民生產總值，工業佔了46.4％，其次是服務業（37.1％）和農業（16.5％）。但在國民就業結構中，服務業自2010年起是印度尼西亞最多人從事的產業，佔48.9％，其次為農業（38.3％）和工業（12.8％）<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.indexmundi.com/indonesia/economy_profile.html |title=Indonesia Economy Profile 2011 |publisher=Indexmundi.com |accessdate=2011-04-10 |archive-date=2021-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814111049/https://www.indexmundi.com/indonesia/economy_profile.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而農業則是過去數世紀最多人從事的產業<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://countrystudies.us/indonesia/64.htm |title=Indonesia - AGRICULTURE |publisher=Countrystudies.us |accessdate=2011-04-10 |archive-date=2017-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171114104011/http://countrystudies.us/indonesia/64.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.childpolicyintl.org/countries/indonesia.html |title=Clearinghouse Countries: Indonesia |publisher=Childpolicyintl.org |accessdate=2011-04-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110410112317/http://www.childpolicyintl.org/countries/indonesia.html |archivedate=2011-04-10 }}</ref>。

